import React, { Component } from 'react'

import Nav from './components/PageElements/Nav'
import FullHeightBanner from './components/PageElements/FullHeightBanner'
import JoinFlip from './components/PageElements/JoinFlip'
import OurCulture from './components/PageElements/OurCulture'
/* import FunEvents from './components/PageElements/FunEvents' */
import Testimonials from './components/PageElements/Testimonials'

import 'bulma/css/bulma.css'
import './css/flip-careers.scss'

class App extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <React.Fragment>
        <Nav />
        <FullHeightBanner />
        <JoinFlip />
        <OurCulture />
        {/* <FunEvents /> */}
        <Testimonials
          icon=""
          authorname="SivaKumar RV"
          description="FLIP is not just a place of work; it’s a WAY OF LIFE! We represent India via our multi-cultural and multi-lingual team – from 16 states and speaking 12 languages. There is Unity in Diversity in our ‘Little India.’ We value every ethnicity and learn from each other. Here are the guiding principles for every FLIPian."
        />
      </React.Fragment>
    )
  }
}

export default App
